Device Spec
Device: iPhone 15 Pro Max
Screen: 393 × 852 px
Design: Rounded corners (54 px), Dynamic Island
Status bar: Full system icons (signal, WiFi, battery)

Interaction Design
Tap a node → bottom sheet slides up (iOS-style detail panel)
Tap again → sheet collapses
Week selector updates all views (fully synced)
Smooth toggle between Thread Map view and Chat view



